{"title":"Collection of 2000+ Free Science Images from the NIH","link":"https://kottke.org/24/10/collection-of-2000-free-science-images-from-the-nih","date":1730321458000,"content":"\n        <p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-04.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-04.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-04.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"872\" alt=\"screenshot of the NIH scientific images site that shows thumbnails of the images in categories like viruses, anatomy, and proteins\" /></p>\n\n<p>From the NIH, <a href=\"https://bioart.niaid.nih.gov/\">a collection of 2,000+ public domain science and medical art visuals</a> (molecules, plants, viruses, proteins, brushes for repeating items like DNA, fungi, equipment‚Ä¶). High-resolution, free to use ‚Äî scientists on social media seem pretty pumped about this.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1386\" alt=\"scientific image\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1302\" alt=\"scientific image\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-03.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/nih-images-03.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"698\" alt=\"scientific image\" /></p>\n\n<p>See also <a href=\"https://www.phylopic.org/\">PhyloPic</a>, a collection of 10,000 ‚Äúfree silhouette images of animals, plants, and other life forms, available for reuse under Creative Commons licenses‚Äù. (via <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/waldo.net\">@waldo.net</a>)</p>\n\n        \n\n         <p><strong>Tags:</strong> <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/art\">art</a> ¬∑ <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/science\">science</a></p>\n\n         <p>üí¨ <a href=\"https://kottke.org/24/10/collection-of-2000-free-science-images-from-the-nih\">Join the discussion on kottke.org</a> ‚Üí</p>\n\n    ","author":"Jason Kottke","siteTitle":"Kottke","siteHash":"89a883271b4598f9b33ebe87be70d38557bcd266e68aee521a8f93622e0ab723","entryHash":"0142cfd5f4acb915a1920e6da0ed5f20c81bf04eee75f9a555c4f95ddbe9ad9c","category":"Sites"}